### Patch 5: Grader Tier-3 Tightening

#### [MODIFY] [grader.py](file:///home/Muaz/Documents/Software/MetaHack/graders/grader.py)

**Line 263:** Require ≥2 keyword matches instead of 1:

```diff
-            if any(kw in joined_agent for kw in gt_keywords):
+            matching_kw = sum(1 for kw in gt_keywords if kw in joined_agent)
+            if matching_kw >= 2:
                 matched += 1
```

