### Patch 6: GRPO Auto-Revert (Entropy Heartbeat)

#### [MODIFY] [train_grpo.py](file:///home/Muaz/Documents/Software/MetaHack/train_grpo.py)

GRPO has no auto-revert logic (PPO does). Add collapse detection + checkpoint revert after the stats block (~line 487):

- Save stable state when entropy > 0.05 and score > 0.3
- Detect collapse: entropy < 0.01 for 2 iterations OR KL > 10 OR score ≤ 0 for 2 iterations
- Revert: reload stable weights, bump entropy_coef and temperature, rebuild optimizer

This mirrors the PPO auto-revert at [train_ppo.py:770-857](file:///home/Muaz/Documents/Software/MetaHack/train_ppo.py#L770-L857).

